FBIS3-16678 "drsov053_e_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-053 Document Type:Daily Report 17 Mar 1994 UKRAINE International Affairs Shmarov, U.S. Envoy Discuss Upcoming Perry Visit WS1703210294 Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network in Ukrainian 2000 GMT 17 Mar 94 WS1703210294 Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network Language: Ukrainian Article Type:BFN [Text] Today, Deputy Prime Minister Valeriy Shmarov held a meeting with William Miller, ambassador extraordinary and plenipotentiary of the United States to Ukraine. During the meeting, which was held in an atmosphere of mutual understanding and good will, a range of pressing issues concerning the upcoming visit of U.S. Secretary of Defense William Perry to Ukraine were discussed. The parties exchanged opinions on the results of the recent Ukrainian-U.S. talks at the highest level.
